726730f-a.title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - 59th Road
726730f-a.text:
Fresh Pond Road, east side, between 59th Road and 59th Drive, showing
the Company home occupied by one Freeman, who was superintendent of Alden
Sampson and Sons Oil Cloth factory.
1922.
Eagene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
